\"http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=18785349&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D18785349%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26page%3D1&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=898dc78d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=18785349&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香討個邊既分析帖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26154875&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D26154875%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=25d39355\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26154875&amp;extra=page%3D1</a> </div>"},{"pid":"ef1de38c14d8192aa4bbf720f745cd97ed371267","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">若果CD-ROM想加入群組的話<br />\n<br />\n可以自行去Uwants 開個新帳號<br />\n<br />\n之後再按照格式PM老夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(CD-ROM即是沒有高登帳號的人士) </div>"},{"pid":"41df9680f66455b50c4887daa151acbdf97587d9","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Facebook 專頁現已開設,諸君可以到專頁留言/讚好/追蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搜尋字眼:黃金帝老夫<br />\n<br />\n連結:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%B8%9D%E8%80%81%E5%A4%AB-384598118583453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B8%259D%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A4%25AB-384598118583453&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=f7969d9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%B8%9D%E8%80%81%E5%A4%AB-384598118583453</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/a0sqbznu7/facebook.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2Fa0sqbznu7%2Ffacebook.jpg&h=961354ba&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7fac4d0de6c93db79341e0e22524a26ee8ef5eb7","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n價位自2月8日開始運行上落市         其後一直處於膠著的狀態<br />\n<br />\n2月23日出現大陽燭突破250天WMA及三角形的頂部後<br />\n<br />\n2月24日繼續冉冉上升<br />\n<br />\n現時價位已突破Keltner Channel 頂線,指示價位正在運行第三浪的後半浪<br />\n<br />\n至於第三浪的終點,則是和之前的計算一樣         此浪應該會升至1338.26才有機會開始回落<br />\n<br />\n估計此浪仍需要2個星期左右才會到達浪頂<br />\n<br />\n基本策略仍是繼續買上    不要螳螂擋車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/89wht6r5h/12331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2F89wht6r5h%2F12331.jpg&h=fb3aff70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf7a49071438028b44729b2973d4ff1b78b00aff","tid":133248,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"終於過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f03cdc02c7d39432f2782c05cc85cfac14b23f2","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n價位昨天跌穿20天WMA後收復失地,其後形態演變為十字星/上升鎚<br />\n<br />\n現時價位在250天WMA及日本雲層圖轉勢線反覆穿梭上落<br />\n<br />\n但繼續是依20天WMA及Raff Regression Channel 反彈<br />\n<br />\n留意下行空間應該不會太大     未來仍是趁低吸納為主<br />\n<br />\n今天估計價位會按Keltner Channel 中軸及20天WMA反彈<br />\n<br />\n所以仍是繼續買上    上升浪仍未完結<br />\n<br />\n現時不太適合沽貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃金每日一單:<br />\n<br />\n現時為2017年3月2日下午7:07分       買入價位為1244.1         建議買入黃金<br />\n<br />\n止賺:1252.1                     止蝕:1249.1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對沖策略:<br />\n<br />\n買入:1244.1             止賺:1252.1             止蝕:1239.1<br />\n<br />\n賣出:1243.6             止賺:1236.9             止蝕:1238.6<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HN8pl5Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHN8pl5Z.jpg&h=2133a892&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4937e6d4861f9b7a42aa1638b7cf2d385699dde5","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"更新群組的討論守則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.禁止在群組作出商業性的宣傳廣告<br />\n<br />\n2.禁止任何垃圾畜牲經紀混入成員當中 <br />\n<br />\n3.禁止任何人向老夫/其他成員求助,有任何麻煩的話請自行解決 (例如不能出金 , 公司有問題等等)<br />\n<br />\n老夫及任何成員不會提供任何協助<br />\n<br />\n4.禁止把群組成員的資料及私隱外洩給外人<br />\n<br />\n5.禁止披露群組對話予外人<br />\n<br />\n6.不能態度惡劣,對老夫/其他群組成員不敬 :<br />\n<br />\n7.禁止私下騷擾成員<br />\n<br />\n8.禁止成員煸動不和諧的討論氣氛<br />\n<br />\n9.老夫保留新增,修改及刪除群組守則的權利, 標準及尺度由老夫自行決定<br />\n<br />\n10.以上守則並不適用於老夫,即老夫不受守則所限"},{"pid":"c178edd51ac4da73b04ea3f9d1c15d580e3c7a66","tid":133248,"uid":441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"想入gp. 返高登pm 你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a924be075584eb9dae67310302693eeddb10962","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n價位於2月27日升至1263.9後出現射擊之星<br />\n<br />\n2月28日出現小陰燭<br />\n<br />\n3月1日雖然出現小陽線,但3月2日出現大陰燭跌穿10天,20天及250天WMA<br />\n<br />\n昨天雖然下試基準線,但收市前出現抗跌鎚收復失地<br />\n<br />\n昨天那支抗跌鎚有可能指示價位會在下周開始第五浪<br />\n<br />\n若果價位再出現急跌,並跌穿第一浪浪頂的話,則有可能運行A浪<br />\n<br />\n下周先繼續買上,但再出大陰燭跌穿基準線的話,那就要果斷投降<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7LJ8335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7LJ8335.jpg&h=ad3a1f01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b32f59015a13f544140235db7fec69a547ce4b6","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"鑑於再次有畜牲經紀潛伏在群組<br />\n<br />\n並把大量的個人資料及群組對話外洩<br />\n<br />\n稍後夜晚10:00正會進行肅清<br />\n<br />\n各成員需把自己的學生證/職員證  連同  身份證一同拍攝給老夫<br />\n<br />\n亦可以提交其他極度有力的證據,以證明自己不是畜牲經紀<br />\n<br />\n感謝諸君的合作,讓我們共創良好的討論環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6591eb2d641d9cda6973dae218f9c7582f9629","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n價位現時已跌穿Bollinger Bands,Keltner Channel 底線<br />\n<br />\n亦已經跌穿日本雲層圖轉勢線及基準線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1,2,3,4,5浪估計已經走完,價位應該在2月27日已運行a浪下跌浪<br />\n<br />\n此個循環的b浪估計是走0.5倍,但現時走去搏反彈好像比較冒險<br />\n<br />\n3月12日雖然出現小陽燭,但昨天無法延縜升勢,並且繼續受壓於100天WMA<br />\n<br />\n加上5條WMA全部向下推移,而剛剛亦出現死亡交叉<br />\n<br />\n暫時不要去搏反彈,現時可以試試輕倉沽貨<br />\n<br />\n亦可以等到確認B浪展開之時,再用黃金比率去計算B浪終點<br />\n<br />\n其後在B浪終點再考慮沽貨會比較合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃金每日一單:<br />\n<br />\n現時為2017年3月14日夜晚9:08分       賣出價位為1203.9         建議沽出黃金<br />\n<br />\n止賺:1195.3                     止蝕:1208.9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對沖策略:<br />\n<br />\n買入:1204.4             止賺:1215.9             止蝕:1199.4<br />\n<br />\n賣出:1203.9             止賺:1195.3             止蝕:1208.9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53L247q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53L247q.jpg&h=cea5091b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2337d4fa0ac8e506d56ffb7e6c0855da915d4ed6","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n因為3月16日公佈利率決議的結果,價位受到該消息影響,出現大陽燭突破10天及100天WMA<br />\n<br />\n翌日則出現抗升鎚升穿20天及50天WMA<br />\n<br />\n但留意昨天的升勢開始減弱,C浪應該很快步會開展/已經開展<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nB浪的起點是3月10日的低位1194.9<br />\n<br />\n而A浪的波幅69  (1263.9-1194.9)<br />\n<br />\n若果運用黃金比率去計算B浪升幅的話,會發現價位差不多已經到頂<br />\n<br />\n1194.9+69*0.236       =1211.2 (Rejected)<br />\n<br />\n1194.9+69*0.382       =1221.3 (Rejected)<br />\n<br />\n1194.9+69*0.5           =1229.4<br />\n<br />\n1194.9+69*0.618       =1237.5<br />\n<br />\n1194.9+69*0.786       =1249.1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鑑於B浪反彈浪是必定會按黃金比率運行,所以現時不值得買上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而價位這兩天亦受壓於Keltner Channel 頂線,Raff Regression Channel及日本雲層圖基準線<br />\n<br />\n所以C浪有可能於星期四以抗升鎚的形態而開展<br />\n<br />\n故未來的策略為不停沽貨,直至本個循環結束為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n至於C浪會於何時結束?  C浪的終點是如何計算?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上兩個問題留待諸君思考<br />\n<br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ace862a8b3176568ca576d1b894f809d497ef05","tid":133248,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1d4R9S5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1d4R9S5.jpg&h=88c44114&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z86849b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz86849b.jpg&h=286529f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVbBK6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVbBK6g.jpg&h=f46b4790&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6spqDUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6spqDUJ.jpg&h=0dbbda91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/124353_cf441d405e14c1c25d740fe933685bb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F124353_cf441d405e14c1c25d740fe933685bb7.jpg&h=1f898471&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"643f75c5e310005dd3da7ad008c2a33ac23adc8d","tid":133248,"uid":16756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:28:10.000Z","msg":"福來村老灣留名"},{"pid":"9e5f46e0bf4f2a91d6227c345971686224c7103e","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n金價雖然升穿Keltner Channel 頂線,但其後連續出2支十字星,似乎無法維持升勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n並且受制於0.786倍黃金比率 (1249.1) , 出現下跌鎚回落至Keltner Channel頂線之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時價位看似會重複之前A浪的下跌方式,兩者都應該是不能企穩250天WMA,並且就此開啟下跌浪     (見下圖)    <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC浪的起點有可能就是3月23日的高位1253.3 , 估計金價未來會再次跌入雲層內部<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃金交叉很快就會出現彈弓手,未來的入市策略仍是不停沽貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直至金價開展一個新的循環為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於本個循環何時會終結?  C浪的終點是多少? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還是那句,諸君想知道答案的話,請運用黃金比率自行計算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CD08KL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCD08KL0.jpg&h=48e35eab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"488b21a2839c3c65e4692ecc0bc63b1b47de044a","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\nBollinger Bands於3月27日出現沽貨訊號<br />\n<br />\n其後價位於3月28日亦跌回入Keltner Channel頂線以下<br />\n<br />\n3月30日出現陰燭跌穿10天WMA<br />\n<br />\n3月31日跌至250天WMA (1240.2)時卻開始止跌回升   但仍受壓於日本雲層圖轉勢線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現時金價貌似正打造雙頂回落 (2月27日的1263.9及3月27日的1261.1)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n此個循環的B浪看來是反彈接近100%再回落,但由於B浪的終點沒有升穿A浪的起點,所以波浪的形態並沒有被破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時金價應該於3月27日運行C浪,而C浪大約會於5月初結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n若果未來金價升穿1263.9的話,那就代表波浪的形態扭曲,C浪下跌浪(破壞性下跌浪)會扭曲為第三浪(爆炸性上浪) (情況和總統大選相於,當時第三浪轉為C浪,循環強行延長)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下週的入市策略為繼續沽貨,但若果價位突破1263.9的話,可以反手買上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n短炒的話,可以先輕倉沽貨,目標看1236.6 (Raff Regression Channel 底線及雲層頂部)<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長擺的話,則要用黃金比率計算跌幅終點<br />\n<br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bdd91a9003813fa88d7cd1f8b130ae9c5a3eb4","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T07:58:53.000Z","msg":"補圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R01420D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR01420D.jpg&h=6c7d4af2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d03f5e8be43066cd25e520c0766694c1c93d45a5","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n因特朗普突破下令射敍利亞發射約60支導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n避險需要上升     金價早上出現大陽燭突破2月27日的高位1263.9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其後夜晚非農數據做差     導致金價進一步攀升至1270.6<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但價位受制於Keltner Channel 頂線,其後出現射擊之星回回落至10天WMA及Keltner Channel中軸附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現時可以確認波浪的形態已經扭曲   <br />\n<br />\n 即是ABC下跌浪會轉為爆炸性上升浪(第三浪)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後市升幅暫先看1338.2   (1.618倍黃金比率)<br />\n<br />\n1180.44+(1220.1-1122.6)*1.618  =1338.2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但留意星期五那支射擊之星顯示沽壓比較重<br />\n<br />\n星期一也有可能出現陰燭回落      支持位暫時看250天WMA的1240.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下週的入市策略訂為逄低買上    不太建議沽貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金價正沿250天WMA及20天WMA作出反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04Uz12q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04Uz12q.jpg&h=66f1c0e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08f8116f9ef22318392cd11ddb987d17fd99333e","tid":133248,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10a6c87ef8da1f3184829352b215041b3fdcf885","tid":133248,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n金價今早一開市後呈現膠著的狀態<br />\n<br />\n現時慢版隨機指數及威廉指標出現沽貨訊號<br />\n<br />\n而星期五亦出現射擊之星,等會金價可能會跌後升<br />\n<br />\n但跌幅有限,估計價位今天是不會跌穿250天WMA<br />\n<br />\n可以趁低買上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃金每日一單:<br />\n<br />\n現時為2017年4月10日下午5:20分      買入價位為1254.1        建議執行以下指令    (有效時間至明天早上7點)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Buy Limit&quot;<br />\n<br />\n價位:1250.1<br />\n<br />\n止蝕:1245.1<br />\n<br />\n止賺:1262.4<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuFE1A0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F